title: Black & Decker The Complete Guide to Outdoor Carpentry
description:
Black & Decker The Complete Guide to Outdoor Carpentry: More than 40 Projects Including by Editors of CPI


Outdoor carpentry projects using cedar, redwood, and pressure-treated pine are perfect for DIYers of all skill levels, since the materials are easy to work with, and the results are rewarding. 

This book features more than 50 projects that easily can be built in a weekend with ordinary power hand tools and materials available at any local home center or hardware store. Each project has complete construction plans and directions for foolproof results.

Genre: Non-Fiction | Educational
